We will be meeting this week, TODAY, MONDAY 11/25 at 5pm in KRESGE 2420.

If you were part of the album swap, come ready to discuss both your selection and your received album, and if not, come anyway and hang out!

Last week on Music Tasting Club...

Archie's album, Alfredo by Freddie Gibbs and The Alchemist is a collaboration between rapper Freddie Gibbs and hip-hop producer The Alchemist. (The title ("Alfredo") is a portmanteau of their names ðŸ¤¯.) Archie first discovered this album from the artwork in the back of a YouTube video, and used his expert searching skills to find the album itself. Released in 2020 during the height of the Black Lives Matter protests, this album features social commentary alongside crazy bars, beautiful instrumentals on tracks like Scottie Beam and 1985, and features from Rick Ross, Tyler, the Creator, Benny the Butcher and Conway the Machine.
